			<pre>
Foo_BAR := 1
			</pre>
			<h2>Compliant Solution</h2>
			<pre>
fooBar := 1
FooBar:=1//or if the var is exported
			</pre>

			<h2>See</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<a href="https://github.com/golang/lint/blob/master/lint.go#L517">github.com</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://golang.org/doc/effective_go.html">golang.org</a>
				</li>
